{"id":640793,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/04/【立此存照】酷玩实验室：洋垃圾分类图鉴/","date":"2020-04-06T09:33:24Z","modified":"2020-04-07T06:00:00Z","title":"【立此存照】酷玩实验室：洋垃圾分类图鉴","content":"<p>近日，微信公众号 @酷玩实验室 转发了 @锦鲤青年 的一则漫画作品，作品中以对“防疫工作中的洋垃圾”分类为名，刻意煽动仇外情绪和种族主义，例如将“黑中国”的外国人分类为“湿垃圾”，将“大闹酒店”的外籍球员分类为“可回收垃圾”等，该漫画也引起了海外英文用户的注意：</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Another sign of soaring xenophobia in China. A cartoon imagines foreigners as trash to be sorted. It invents their crimes against the virus response, mixes it with their malign motives in China, and fantasizes about committing violence against them. <a href=\"https://t.co/5G7TuAMWKO\">https://t.co/5G7TuAMWKO</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/Y2ZjNagvKl\">pic.twitter.com/Y2ZjNagvKl</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Paul Mozur 孟建国 (@paulmozur) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/paulmozur/status/1247025734146613249?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 6, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p><strong>以下为原文全文：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/洋垃圾-scaled.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-640794\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/洋垃圾-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"2270\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/洋垃圾-scaled.jpg 564w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/洋垃圾-66x300.jpg 66w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/洋垃圾-768x3485.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/洋垃圾-338x1536.jpg 338w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/洋垃圾-451x2048.jpg 451w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/洋垃圾2-1-scaled.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-640795\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/洋垃圾2-1-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" wid